  {w:"vestige",s:"The only <strong>vestige</strong> of the original school building that remained standing was a single stone archway the architects had deliberately preserved.",p:"noun",d:"A trace of something that once existed.",e:"The only vestige of the old school building left standing was a single stone archway the new design had preserved."},
